Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.65,0:29:18.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}空っぽになって
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.65,0:29:18.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}恍然间虚无一片
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.19,0:29:21.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,100)}僕らは箱の中
